#2000
Floating High Above Lamman~
   Behold!  You stand at the brink of high adventure, pulse quickening
danger, and magnificent treasures beyond your grandest dreams.  By some strange
cosmic force you have materialized here: the gateway to the vast realm known as
the Archipelago!
   Looking around, you are surprised to discover yourself standing on a
grayish-white cloud floating high above the ground.  Although standing here in
the clouds is quite cozy and safe, you begin to feel restless and look for a
way down from the sky.  Far below, you see a bubbling marble fountain in the
middle of the busy Market Square of the great harbour city of Lamman.  A
slender golden rope will help assist in your descent down.
~
20 36996 0
D5
A slender golden rope leads down to a fountain and the Market Square.
~
~
