E
cloud~
   The cloud is thick and puffy.  Inscribed on one corner of the cloud, as
if inscribed in stone, you notice a map of the city.~
E
rope slender golden~
  The rope is braided from hundreds of fine gold strands.  It leads down
through the clouds to the city of Lamman below.  It looks incredibly strong,
able to support the heaviest of giants.
~
S
#2001
The Central Fountain~
   This is the central hub of the entire market place.  It is dominated by an
imposing marble basin, into which water flows from a large statue of rather
dubious artistic merit.  Among the carefully cut flagstones surrounding the
fountain is a squarish block of polished granite inscribed with a map. It
seems so peaceful here with the %2gentle murmur of business activity all
around, the occasional nicker of horses as they drink from the fountain and
the %merry burble of water as it flows into the basin.  It's really a shame
you can't stay here all the time.
~
