#2003
East Market Square~
      This is the eastern portion of Lamman's market square. Just to the east
hangs the shingle of Sigur the Blacksmith. A bit to the north you can make 
the Temple of Lamman, whilst to the west lies the fountain surrounded as ever
by dangerous looking adventurers.
~
