#2008
Northwest Market Square~
   The northwest corner of market square is traditionally where public
humiliations and the occasional public execution are carried out.  To the
west residents of the Warrior's Widow -- the finest inn in Lamman, get fine
views of the fun from their bedroom windows.  The city's central fountain is
to the southeast.
~
