#2009
Southeast Market Square~
   This is the southeastern corner of Lamman's market square.  It is busy
here on the cobblestone street.  The rich and poor alike stroll the market
searching for bargains from the many merchants and traders who have set up
shop here.  Almost obscured from view, on the ground, is a squarish block of
polished granite inscribed with a map.  To the south lies Harbour Road.  The
market square extends to the north and west.
~
