S
#2011
Sigur's Armour Repair Smithy~
   Everyone knows that dwarves make the best blacksmiths, something to do with
surface area to volume ratios or some such thing.  To be sure, in Lamman the
blacksmiths are all dwarves.  No one is sure exactly how this came to be, but
some time ago a few trolls tried to set up a rival smithy in the heart of the
Troll Quarter.  Rumour has it there was an accident one night, and they were
found melted down in their own forge the next morning.
   Sigur is usually to be found here in his shop shaping steel plates into
armour for the City Watch.  By virtue of his skill at smithing armour, he has
a contract to forge armours for the King and the city guard.  Of course, a lack
of competition more than encourages it.  Despite a regular income, he still
insists in making a little extra coin on the side, and if not busy with other
things repairs the armour of adventurers in need.
~
