#2012
Hurgoods House of Armour~
      You are standing in the finest armoury in all of Lamman, at least that's
what Hurgood always says.  All manner of armour adorns the wall, armour for bits
of the body you never imagined needed armour and some for bits of the body you
can't imagine having! Hurgood himself is sitting at a bench hammering dents
from a breastplate.
~
