S
#2013
Jurt's Weapons of War~
      This place is packed from floor to ceiling with more types of vicious
weaponry than you have ever seen in your life. Many of the weapons you can
only guess at their purpose and supress a shudder. Jurt is standing in the 
back of the shop, calmly adding a killing edge to a huge axe. The grinding
wheel shoots sparks everywhere.
~
