S
#2016
The Reception of the Warrior's Widow Inn~
   This is the cozy reception area of the Warrior's Widow Inn.  Many a weary
adventurer comes here after a long days adventuring, safe in the knowledge
that his or her valuables will be well guarded.  However, this sort of service
doesn't come cheap, perhaps that note on the counter is the Inn's tariff.
~
