#2031
The Proving Grounds~
   The practice field is a marked-off sandy square of roughly 20' by 20'.  The
room is huge, the large mortared stone blocks of the city walls forming the back
wall of the grounds.  Banners hang from the walls, representing the various
mercenary companies allied with the city and various racks are evenly spaced
around the room to hold weapons not in use.  The Master of the Warrior's Guild
is usually to be found here, training the city guard and other aspiring 
novices in the warrior's art.
