#2032
The Lamman Public Library~
   This is a beautiful facility provided by the townsfolk for the betterment
of the general populace.  Here, you can relax unmolested in peace, and catch
up on the latest news, and perhaps learn something new.  The library has many
books available, all of which are chained to rickety wooden shelves to help
prevent theft.  There are also maps displayed on the walls.  One map in
particular catches your eye.  This library exits east onto a wide paved muddy
road.
