#2043
An Odd Room to be a Gaol~
   This strange little room seems out of place in the middle of the Lamman
city goal.  The walls are smooth and polished.  The floor is constructed from
sturdy planks.  Strangely, however, you feel as if you are being closely
watched.  Someone may be lurking here in the shadows.  The only way out of
this small room is the portal to the north and an odd trapdoor in the floor.
