#2049
The Watch House~
   The boot steps of the city watch echo off the cold slate flagstones that
pave Lamman's northern gateway.  Occasionally, one of these stalwart keepers
of the peace stop inside this small, cramped office and file a report.  Row
upon row of pigeonholes cover the entire back wall, each overflowing with
paperwork.  Despite the chaos and clutter, this building serves its function:
as an administration center and occasionally an overflow gaol.
