#2068
The Quay~
   This is the eastern end of the city of Lamman's Quay.  To the south lies
the office of the harbour master, which is the place to negotiate passage on
a ship.  The Quay extends west from here.  You have never seen so many exotic
looking boats and people in one place.  The harbour area is notoriously rough,
the city watch usually maintains only a token presence to quell major riots.
To aid the one unfamiliar with this part of the city, a beautiful granite map
stone has been embedded into the ground here.  If you're wandering around here,
you had better watch your back, and not to get lost.  Lime street runs north
from here into the dwarven section of town.
