S
#2083
Durrin's Weapon Reapair Shop~
   Everyone knows that dwarves make the best blacksmiths, something to do with
surface area to volume ratios or some such thing.  To be sure, in Lamman the
blacksmiths are all dwarves.  No one is sure exactly how this came to be, but
some time ago a few trolls tried to set up a rival smithy in the heart of the
Troll Quarter.  Rumor has it there was an accident one night, and they were
found melted down in their own forge the next morning.
   Durrin can usually be found here in his shop.  As the official blacksmith
of Lamman, he turns a tidy profit repairing weapons and crafting arms for the
King.  When not too busy, he makes a bit of spare coin on the side repairing
weapons for adventurers.
~
20 8 0
D0
You see Sigur's smithy.
~
