#2084
Harbour Road~
   The aptly named Harbour Road runs alongside the busy harbour front.  As
you look south across the picturesque bay, you see ships of all sizes riding
at anchor in the calm waters.  To the west, you see the famous Red Bridge of
Lamman.  Harbour Road continues on to the east.
~
